age:EN-GB;\r\n     mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Pregnancy problems, post-natal care.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\n     mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\n     EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">It can also be used to help with the following:<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n     mso-add-space:auto;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n     Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\n     mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Recovery from chronic or acute symptoms,</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\n     mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\n     EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n     mso-add-space:auto;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n     Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\n     mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Restore energy and the balance of their\r\n     physical and emotional health,</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n     12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n     Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\n     mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n     mso-add-space:auto;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n     Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\n     mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Rebuild a healthy lifestyle and the feeling of\r\n     wellbeing.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n     150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n     mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\n     EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#1D2228;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Does acupuncture hurt?</span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">Acupuncture rarely \'<b>hurts</b>\'. The most that people experience is a\r\ndull ache around the base of the inserted needle, or a slight tingling feeling\r\nwhen the needle is inserted. Points at the extremities, like toe or finger\r\nends, can sometimes be a little sharp, but the sensation is usually brief.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2019-04-20 18:54:17', '2019-04-24 13:04:04');
INSERT INTO `services` (`id`, `title`, `main_description`, `sub_description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(28, 'Deep tissue Massage', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">Deep tissue massage is a type of massage therapy that focuses on\r\nrealigning deeper layers of muscles and connective tissue. It is especially\r\nhelpful for chronic aches and pains and contracted areas such as stiff neck and\r\nupper back, low back pain, leg muscle tightness, and sore shoulders.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">Some of the same strokes are used as classic massage therapy, but the\r\nmovement is slower and the pressure is deeper and concentrated on areas of\r\ntension and pain in order to reach the sub-layer of muscles and the fascia (the\r\nconnective tissue surrounding muscles).</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">How Does It Work?\r\nTechniques</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">When there is chronic muscle tension or injury, there are usually\r\nadhesions (bands of painful, rigid tissue) in muscles, tendons, and ligaments.\r\nAdhesions can block circulation and cause pain, limited movement, and\r\ninflammation.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">Deep tissue massage works by physically breaking down these adhesions to\r\nrelieve pain and restore normal movement. To do this, the massage therapist\r\nuses massage oil and often uses direct deep pressure. Muscles must be relaxed\r\nin order for the therapist to reach the deeper musculature.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Does Deep Tissue Massage\r\nHurt?</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">At certain points during the massage, most people find there is usually\r\nsome discomfort and pain.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">It is important to tell the massage therapist when things hurt and if\r\nany soreness or pain you experience is outside your comfort range.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">There is usually some stiffness or pain after a deep tissue massage, but\r\nit should subside within a day or so. The massage therapist may recommend\r\napplying ice to the area after the massage.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Benefits of Deep Tissue\r\nMassage:</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-GB\">Deep tissue massage usually focuses on a specific problem, such as\r\nchronic muscle pain, injury rehabilitation, and the following conditions:</span><span 